                            <comment id="12622821" author="hossman" created="Fri, 15 Aug 2008 07:49:43 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Note: this bug was introduced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-470&quot; title=&quot;DateField throws error on iso8601 date&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-470&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-470&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

